# Database
*.db
# … except the read-only reference DB used by /houses, /planets, /zodiac.
# Stable, hand-curated content; ships with the deploy.
# audit.db (Neon-replaced legacy SQLite log) stays ignored.
!backend/vedic_astrology.db

# Pickle / serialized files
*.pkl
# … except the pre-built embedding indexes, which are stable artifacts
# bundled with the deploy and rebuilt only when source data changes.
!backend/dict_embeddings.pkl
!backend/search_index.pkl

